snippet.textDisplay: I'm not saying a reunion isn't possible, but I'm not a fanatic. Yes, I fell apart as a teenager when they broke up, but as a thirty something divorced woman, I see the world differently. Sometimes you can meet the right person at the wrong time & get along better as a couple when you're both older. I see it all the time. Whether or not it happens with Jen & Brad remains to be seen, but it's good they can at least walk away from the past & be friends.
